headline: Anne Wojcicki’s nonprofit reaches deal to acquire 23andMe
summary: Beleaguered genetic testing company 23andMe announced Friday that it has reached an agreement to sell itself to TTAM Research Institute, a nonprofit led by the company's co-founder and former CEO Anne Wojcicki.

headline: Amgen: Imdelltra Data And Q1 Results Impress
summary: Amgen beat Q1 estimates with strong margins driven by Blincyto, Prolia, and standout Imdelltra growth, plus strength in obesity. See why AMGN stock is a buy.
